{"tid":1980951,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［建造業基金］減薪就有我份 抗疫基金冇我份","createTime":"2020-04-20T11:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T01:14:09.000Z","uid":255150,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2343eb980b3e6e28398791f2004818f9a8555c5c","tid":1980951,"uid":255150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:40:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我係垃圾AE仔 畢業到而家做左兩年 係間垃圾sub仔到做<br />\n咁本來就做緊政府盤 之前地盤就停工<br />\n我就由2月份WFH開始比垃圾公司減撚左人工<br />\n做AE仔又唔會無啦啦申請工人註冊證 得兩年經驗又乜牌都冇 得張垃圾綠卡 <br />\n<br />\n我個fd之前是撚但返左一日地盤就唔做 <br />\n轉左行做長工 工又有得返 錢又收得足<br />\n咁撚樣既人就收撚到足 我真真正正受影響既又乜撚都冇<br />\n<br />\n而家減撚完人工 日日都仲要捱撚住咁過 <br />\n抗疫基金點撚抗疫呀 屌你老母"},{"pid":"436a0e03b6ee0b835ee90036eb46c9830b49152b","tid":1980951,"uid":37733,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:50:15.000Z","msg":"我係e都有申請工人證喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3549bea53010fadef1f2e0f67af03e17c3309228","tid":1980951,"uid":255150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"436a0e03b6ee0b835ee90036eb46c9830b49152b","tid":1980951,"uid":37733,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:50:15.000Z","msg":"我係e都有申請工人證喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:56:16.000Z","msg":"我識好多人都冇整"},{"pid":"a40a9464c6e2b87834b2a98c6b5fe0dbc7445a66","tid":1980951,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3549bea53010fadef1f2e0f67af03e17c3309228","tid":1980951,"uid":255150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"436a0e03b6ee0b835ee90036eb46c9830b49152b","tid":1980951,"uid":37733,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:50:15.000Z","msg":"我係e都有申請工人證喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"